I have just taken the login part of it and changed it to my information. When i go to compile it it gives me an error saying that i need to have JDK 5 or 6. Well they now have 7, so i insterted the 7 folder.

@echo off
if exist “C:\Program Files (x86)” set programfiles=C:\Program Files (x86)
set pro=%programfiles%\Java\jdk1.7.0_07
set pro2=%programfiles%\Java\jdk1.7.0_07
set jac=\bin\javac.exe
set jav=\bin\java.exe

But it still says when i want to compile it that i need JDK 5 or 6, can anyone help me out?
